we love each other." (Laughter)

294
00:13:49,450 --> 00:13:52,592
And I'm a little bit slow,

295
00:13:52,592 --> 00:13:54,503
and I looked around me, and I said,

296
00:13:54,503 --> 00:13:56,805
I thought, maybe, the fence is missing.

297
00:13:56,805 --> 00:13:58,900
Wasn't there a fence here
last time I came?

298
00:13:58,900 --> 00:14:01,958
You know, this big
protective fence around the village,

299
00:14:01,958 --> 00:14:04,672
and they sort of looked at me
